data.name: InfoBox.Text
data.value:
When exporting, select your .../Jedi Fallen Order/SwGame/Content/Paks folder. If you select another folder, you will need to manually move the Pakchunk99_CustomSabercolors.pak file to the Paks folder.
To uninstall, navigate to .../Jedi Fallen Order/SwGame/Content/Paks folder and delete Pakchunk99_CustomSabercolors.pak
